           &mt LALT F9   &mt LCTRL F2  &mt LSHFT F5  &mt LGUI F10    &kp F12                 &kp LEFT          &mt RGUI DOWN      &mt RSHFT UP  &mt RCTRL RIGHT  &kp EQUAL
&kp GRAVE  &kp C_VOL_DN  &kp C_VOL_UP  &kp LS(F5)    &kp LS(LG(N5))  &kp LS(LG(NUMBER_4))    &kp LEFT_BRACKET  &kp RIGHT_BRACKET  &kp LPAR      &kp RPAR         &kp BACKSLASH  &kp C_PP
                                       &trans        &trans          &trans                  &kp BACKSPACE     &kp C_PREV         &ttnextprev
